584
00:25:40,020 --> 00:25:41,500
I should've returned him to you.

585
00:25:41,500 --> 00:25:42,680
It's all my fault.

586
00:25:43,330 --> 00:25:44,330
You're the Prefect's son.

587
00:25:44,770 --> 00:25:45,980
He's your son.

588
00:25:46,500 --> 00:25:47,440
You go tell the Prefect.

589
00:25:47,530 --> 00:25:49,020
He won't ignore him.

590
00:25:54,460 --> 00:25:55,300
Jiangli,

591
00:25:56,260 --> 00:25:57,700
stay calm and listen to me.

592
00:25:58,610 --> 00:26:00,050
Yanyan's identity is special.

593
00:26:00,850 --> 00:26:02,180
If we tell Father now

594
00:26:02,180 --> 00:26:04,020
without a plan,

595
00:26:04,770 --> 00:26:05,740
the Prefect's Mansion

596
00:26:06,460 --> 00:26:07,940
won't be a sanctuary for him.

597
00:26:08,330 --> 00:26:10,260
It will become the most dangerous place.

598
00:26:11,530 --> 00:26:12,370
Jingxiu,

599
00:26:12,950 --> 00:26:13,810
Danling,

600
00:26:13,810 --> 00:26:15,260
and so many unseen enemies.

601
00:26:16,180 --> 00:26:18,190
Not everyone wants
what's best for Yanyan, right?

602
00:26:19,940 --> 00:26:20,780
Maybe

603
00:26:21,770 --> 00:26:23,090
his illness won't be cured,

604
00:26:23,850 --> 00:26:25,370
and we'll put him in greater danger.

605
00:26:26,770 --> 00:26:27,810
Please believe me.

606
00:26:29,130 --> 00:26:30,220
Let's figure this out.

607
00:26:31,460 --> 00:26:32,610
Leave this to me,

608
00:26:33,940 --> 00:26:34,780
alright?

609
00:26:48,090 --> 00:26:49,320
Let's first check on the child.

610
00:27:02,370 --> 00:27:03,610
