617
00:27:17,700 --> 00:27:19,500
I'll get you a chicken leg.

618
00:27:25,980 --> 00:27:26,850
Is it good?

619
00:27:26,850 --> 00:27:27,690
It's delicious.

620
00:27:29,850 --> 00:27:33,460
Let me try a bit.

621
00:27:34,610 --> 00:27:35,940
It's so good.

622
00:27:39,700 --> 00:27:40,850
I didn't expect Jingming

623
00:27:40,850 --> 00:27:42,420
to have a child.

624
00:27:43,090 --> 00:27:43,930
Yeah.

625
00:27:44,180 --> 00:27:45,330
And he's already four.

626
00:27:46,570 --> 00:27:47,770
But this little one

627
00:27:47,770 --> 00:27:49,260
is so likable.

628
00:27:51,770 --> 00:27:52,610
Yanyan...

629
00:27:53,570 --> 00:27:54,980
I felt so sorry for him

630
00:27:55,420 --> 00:27:56,770
when he had his attack today.

631
00:27:57,980 --> 00:27:58,820
By the way,

632
00:27:59,460 --> 00:28:01,610
Jiangli told me today

633
00:28:01,610 --> 00:28:03,330
not to mention anything about Yanyan.

634
00:28:04,610 --> 00:28:05,940
Jingming also told me about it.

635
00:28:08,020 --> 00:28:09,420
Our household is full of gossip.

636
00:28:10,130 --> 00:28:11,980
If people find out

637
00:28:11,980 --> 00:28:13,090
that Jingming has a child,

638
00:28:13,380 --> 00:28:14,260
who knows

639
00:28:14,260 --> 00:28:15,570
what kind of trouble might arise?

640
00:28:17,530 --> 00:28:19,530
We've learned such a big secret.

641
00:28:20,130 --> 00:28:22,130
We must keep it to ourselves.

642
00:28:25,530 --> 00:28:27,220
The envoys from Beizhou and Nanzhou

643
00:28:27,460 --> 00:28:28,810
will visit us

644
00:28:28,810 --> 00:28:30,220
in half a month.

645
00:28:30,370 --> 00:28:31,420
What do you three

646
00:28:31,660 --> 00:28:32,940
think about it?

647
00:28:33,330 --> 00:28:34,170
Father,

648
00:28:34,900 --> 00:28:35,940
I think

649
00:28:36,290 --> 00:28:37,610
that since Beizhou and Nanzhou

650
00:28:38,020 --> 00:28:39,290
rarely interact with us,

651
00:28:39,700 --> 00:28:41,900
their visit now,
when Xizhou is invading us,

652
00:28:42,660 --> 00:28:43,610
must be a probe,

653
00:28:43,770 --> 00:28:44,980
not a simple visit.

654
00:28:45,290 --> 00:28:46,570
They're weighing

655
00:28:46,570 --> 00:28:48,090
whether to support us

656
00:28:48,090 --> 00:28:49,700
or Xizhou.

657
00:28:51,180 --> 00:28:52,020
That's right.

658
00:28:52,420 --> 00:28:53,260
Jingxiu,

659
00:28:53,460 --> 00:28:55,850
what's the use of pointing that out?

660
00:28:56,530 --> 00:28:57,700
Who doesn't know

661
00:28:57,700 --> 00:29:00,020
that the situation
between Xizhou and us is tense,

662
00:29:00,020 --> 00:29:02,050
and Beizhou and Nanzhou
are waiting to pick sides?

663
00:29:03,180 --> 00:29:05,660
Jingxing, haven't you always been idle?

664
00:29:07,610 --> 00:29:08,940
Oh, you're not idle;

665
00:29:08,940 --> 00:29:10,330
you're just sightseeing.

666
00:29:10,770 --> 00:29:12,740
Since when does this lazy young master

667
00:29:12,980 --> 00:29:15,090
care about the world's situation?

668
00:29:15,090 --> 00:29:16,260
The rise and fall of a nation

669
00:29:16,260 --> 00:29:17,430
is everyone's responsibility.

670
00:29:17,610 --> 00:29:19,420
Besides, I'm the young master
of Dongzhou too.

671
00:29:19,660 --> 00:29:21,260
Master Jingxing, tell us

672
00:29:21,460 --> 00:29:22,420
your opinion then.

673
00:29:22,610 --> 00:29:23,810
Since they're coming,

674
00:29:24,090 --> 00:29:24,980
we can't be afraid.

675
00:29:25,180 --> 00:29:26,180
We can just attack.

676
00:29:28,700 --> 00:29:29,540
Jingxing,

677
00:29:30,050 --> 00:29:32,700
we've had many border skirmishes
with Xizhou over the years,

678
00:29:33,180 --> 00:29:34,940
which has drained our resources.

679
00:29:35,260 --> 00:29:37,370
If we go to war with Beizhou
and Nanzhou now,

680
00:29:37,570 --> 00:29:39,260
won't we be attacked from three sides?

681
00:29:40,260 --> 00:29:41,180
Jingxing,

682
00:29:41,180 --> 00:29:43,050
you're more suited for sightseeing.

683
00:29:43,420 --> 00:29:44,530
War

684
00:29:44,940 --> 00:29:46,980
isn't just about talking.

685
00:29:47,180 --> 00:29:48,090
So what?

686
00:29:48,370 --> 00:29:49,610
The men of Dongzhou are strong.

687
00:29:49,850 --> 00:29:51,330
We can fight three enemies at once.

688
00:29:52,290 --> 00:29:53,130
Jingxiu,

689
00:29:53,460 --> 00:29:55,020
you command the Golden Guards.

690
00:29:55,020 --> 00:29:57,020
How can you be so indecisive?

691
00:29:58,020 --> 00:29:59,130
If we waver like this,

692
00:29:59,460 --> 00:30:01,770
Beizhou and Nanzhou will laugh at us,

693
00:30:02,260 --> 00:30:04,330
thinking we're all about the show.

694
00:30:04,500 --> 00:30:06,500
It'll only embolden Xizhou.

695
00:30:07,570 --> 00:30:08,700
Nonsense.

696
00:30:09,130 --> 00:30:09,970
Father,

697
00:30:10,290 --> 00:30:12,500
leave Jingxing out of this from now on.

698
00:30:13,660 --> 00:30:15,330
Should I be left out

699
00:30:15,570 --> 00:30:16,810
because I disagree with Jingxiu?

700
00:30:17,310 --> 00:30:18,180
Father,

701
00:30:18,180 --> 00:30:20,530
since when has Jingxiu
taken charge of Dongzhou?

702
00:30:20,700 --> 00:30:22,810
Enough. Be quiet now.

703
00:30:24,860 --> 00:30:25,700
Jingxing,

704
00:30:25,700 --> 00:30:26,740
although you're young,

705
00:30:26,980 --> 00:30:28,130
as a young master,

706
00:30:28,270 --> 00:30:29,900
you should be careful with your words.

707
00:30:31,850 --> 00:30:33,610
- Jingxiu.
- Yes.

708
00:30:33,610 --> 00:30:34,770
The Golden Guards

709
00:30:34,980 --> 00:30:36,460
haven't improved in ability

710
00:30:36,700 --> 00:30:38,370
but have caused many problems.

711
00:30:38,370 --> 00:30:39,420
There are always complaints

712
00:30:39,420 --> 00:30:41,460
about them being submitted to me.

713
00:30:41,460 --> 00:30:43,180
How are you managing the Golden Guards?

714
00:30:43,180 --> 00:30:44,020
Father,

715
00:30:44,330 --> 00:30:45,700
there must be a misunderstanding.

716
00:30:46,370 --> 00:30:47,210
Father, don't worry.

717
00:30:47,610 --> 00:30:48,850
This time, when the envoys come,

718
00:30:49,260 --> 00:30:51,050
the Golden Guards will shine

719
00:30:51,370 --> 00:30:52,660
to demonstrate our power.

720
00:30:54,850 --> 00:30:55,900
Good.

721
00:31:01,810 --> 00:31:02,650
Jingming,

722
00:31:04,290 --> 00:31:06,500
why are you so quiet today?

723
00:31:07,770 --> 00:31:08,700
I believe

724
00:31:09,180 --> 00:31:10,290
that our forces are

725
00:31:10,570 --> 00:31:11,660
about the same as Xizhou's,

726
00:31:12,090 --> 00:31:13,220
and so is our grain supply.

727
00:31:13,660 --> 00:31:14,810
If we go to war,

728
00:31:15,260 --> 00:31:16,460
what will make the difference

729
00:31:16,980 --> 00:31:18,220
is the quality of our weapons.

730
00:31:19,850 --> 00:31:20,810
Good.

731
00:31:20,810 --> 00:31:21,650
Go on.

732
00:31:22,460 --> 00:31:23,720
Based on the overall situation,

733
00:31:23,850 --> 00:31:25,130
if a war breaks out,

734
00:31:25,770 --> 00:31:27,290
one side will need to improve

735
00:31:27,740 --> 00:31:29,570
its weapons to gain the upper hand.

736
00:31:30,530 --> 00:31:32,500
I think Xizhou

737
00:31:32,500 --> 00:31:33,900
probably realized this years ago.

738
00:31:34,940 --> 00:31:35,980
So, over the years,

739
00:31:36,260 --> 00:31:37,220
Xizhou has been

740
00:31:37,530 --> 00:31:39,180
constantly improving its weapons

741
00:31:39,180 --> 00:31:40,250
and its military strength.

742
00:31:40,940 --> 00:31:42,610
I once sent people to gather information

743
00:31:42,610 --> 00:31:43,980
on the weapons they commonly use

744
00:31:44,370 --> 00:31:45,460
and bought some to study.

745
00:31:46,330 --> 00:31:47,170
I found

746
00:31:47,850 --> 00:31:49,390
that while their weapons are excellent,

747
00:31:49,660 --> 00:31:50,940
they're not so good

748
00:31:51,180 --> 00:31:52,810
that they'd dare to initiate
an invasion.

749
00:31:53,260 --> 00:31:54,100
So,

750
00:31:54,460 --> 00:31:55,300
recently,

751
00:31:55,810 --> 00:31:57,370
with Xizhou becoming so rampant,

752
00:31:58,090 --> 00:31:59,130
it's clear

753
00:31:59,370 --> 00:32:00,220
they must've made

754
00:32:00,220 --> 00:32:01,750
a major breakthrough in their weapons.

755
00:32:03,420 --> 00:32:04,610
Jingming is right.

756
00:32:05,090 --> 00:32:07,460
The key to victory lies in weapons.

757
00:32:07,460 --> 00:32:09,260
I've also ordered my men

758
00:32:09,260 --> 00:32:10,260
to develop a few things,

759
00:32:10,700 --> 00:32:12,980
but I'm not sure
if we can face them in battle.

760
00:32:18,900 --> 00:32:19,740
Father,

761
00:32:20,290 --> 00:32:21,810
are you having a headache again?

762
00:32:24,460 --> 00:32:25,980
Don't worry about my health.

763
00:32:28,370 --> 00:32:29,500
You three,

764
00:32:29,700 --> 00:32:31,260
go back and think carefully.

765
00:32:31,260 --> 00:32:32,570
If, in the end,

766
00:32:32,570 --> 00:32:34,050
our weapons are no match for Xizhou,

767
00:32:34,610 --> 00:32:36,420
how will we win with an unexpected move?

768
00:32:37,900 --> 00:32:38,740
Go to work.

769
00:32:38,940 --> 00:32:39,780
- Yes.
- Yes.

770
00:32:46,290 --> 00:32:47,260
Let's go, Jingming.

771
00:32:56,740 --> 00:32:57,580
Young Master.

772
00:32:57,770 --> 00:32:58,610
How's it going?

773
00:32:58,770 --> 00:32:59,950
We've tried some new methods,

774
00:33:00,130 --> 00:33:01,150
but none of them worked.

775
00:33:01,460 --> 00:33:02,810
When the arrows are shot,

776
00:33:02,810 --> 00:33:04,370
they're either too close or too far off.

777
00:33:05,090 --> 00:33:06,660
We can speed things up now.

778
00:33:06,660 --> 00:33:07,500
Yes.

779
00:33:07,980 --> 00:33:08,820
Jingxing,

780
00:33:09,180 --> 00:33:10,020
do you see?

781
00:33:10,610 --> 00:33:12,940
To make Father happy,
Jingming is working

782
00:33:13,260 --> 00:33:14,840
through the night to make the crossbow.

783
00:33:15,180 --> 00:33:16,260
Don't be fooled

784
00:33:16,260 --> 00:33:18,370
by his calm and collected appearance.

785
00:33:20,090 --> 00:33:21,020
Jingxiu,

786
00:33:21,020 --> 00:33:22,130
you can make weapons too

787
00:33:22,130 --> 00:33:24,180
if you want.

788
00:33:24,330 --> 00:33:25,940
Why complain behind Jingming's back

789
00:33:25,940 --> 00:33:27,770
because you can't make them yourself?

790
00:33:41,980 --> 00:33:42,820
Jingming,

791
00:33:43,260 --> 00:33:45,370
