to ask Father for medicine?

792
00:33:47,740 --> 00:33:48,660
How do you know

793
00:33:48,660 --> 00:33:49,500
I need medicine?

794
00:33:50,770 --> 00:33:52,130
Yanyan's illness is very strange.

795
00:33:52,460 --> 00:33:54,470
It can't be something
ordinary medicine can cure.

796
00:33:55,000 --> 00:33:56,850
Besides, you have various herbs at home.

797
00:33:57,260 --> 00:33:58,530
I saw you were so absent-minded

798
00:33:58,530 --> 00:34:00,020
just now in the hall.

799
00:34:00,260 --> 00:34:01,660
It must be about Yanyan.

800
00:34:02,260 --> 00:34:03,220
So, I guessed

801
00:34:03,220 --> 00:34:04,610
you wanted to ask Father

802
00:34:04,610 --> 00:34:05,810
for medicine to treat Yanyan.

803
00:34:06,220 --> 00:34:07,220
Yanyan's illness

804
00:34:08,500 --> 00:34:09,880
can only be treated with Lei Pill.

805
00:34:11,380 --> 00:34:12,220
Lei Pill?

806
00:34:12,900 --> 00:34:14,820
Jingming, are you out of your mind?

807
00:34:15,130 --> 00:34:16,530
Lei Pill is so precious.

808
00:34:17,730 --> 00:34:19,300
Good thing you didn't speak up just now.

809
00:34:19,940 --> 00:34:20,900
Otherwise,

810
00:34:20,900 --> 00:34:22,760
Father would be furious to see you

811
00:34:22,760 --> 00:34:24,250
not caring about the current situation

812
00:34:24,250 --> 00:34:25,340
but asking for Lei Pill.

813
00:34:25,900 --> 00:34:27,050
Our big brother

814
00:34:27,210 --> 00:34:28,860
wouldn't miss such a good opportunity.

815
00:34:30,690 --> 00:34:31,900
I know I shouldn't do this,

816
00:34:32,940 --> 00:34:34,090
but I have to.

817
00:34:39,220 --> 00:34:43,660
(Rain Chamber)

818
00:35:05,250 --> 00:35:06,460
Give me more time.

819
00:35:19,070 --> 00:35:20,380
I already know about what happened

820
00:35:20,380 --> 00:35:21,780
in the hall today.

821
00:35:23,500 --> 00:35:25,820
The Prefect is already troubled

822
00:35:26,250 --> 00:35:27,850
by the envoys from Beizhou and Nanzhou,

823
00:35:28,300 --> 00:35:29,780
and his headache is getting worse.

824
00:35:31,130 --> 00:35:32,860
If you bring it up now,

825
00:35:33,940 --> 00:35:34,860
it may

826
00:35:35,050 --> 00:35:36,250
backfire

827
00:35:39,530 --> 00:35:41,170
and affect your future prospects.

828
00:35:47,020 --> 00:35:48,460
I want to be the Young Prefect,

829
00:35:48,930 --> 00:35:50,870
but I think Yanyan's illness
is more important.

830
00:35:51,500 --> 00:35:52,380
I plan

831
00:35:53,050 --> 00:35:54,250
to ask Father for Lei Pill

832
00:35:54,610 --> 00:35:55,570
when he's happy

833
00:35:56,020 --> 00:35:57,140
as the crossbow is finished.

834
00:35:57,650 --> 00:35:59,340
But Yanyan's illness can't wait.

835
00:36:00,690 --> 00:36:01,730
I have a plan.

836
00:36:02,170 --> 00:36:03,010
No.

837
00:36:03,210 --> 00:36:04,420
I haven't told you.

838
00:36:04,420 --> 00:36:05,500
I know what you want to do.

839
00:36:06,250 --> 00:36:07,500
All the physicians in the city

840
00:36:07,500 --> 00:36:08,340
are helpless

841
00:36:08,340 --> 00:36:09,280
with Father's illness.

842
00:36:09,730 --> 00:36:11,020
If you rashly try to treat him,

843
00:36:11,300 --> 00:36:12,170
it's too dangerous.

844
00:36:12,300 --> 00:36:13,140
Jingming,

845
00:36:13,860 --> 00:36:15,570
since I cured your hidden illness

846
00:36:17,020 --> 00:36:18,730
and Qingqing's face injury,

847
00:36:19,340 --> 00:36:20,530
I have an 80% chance

848
00:36:20,820 --> 00:36:22,020
of curing Father's illness.

849
00:36:22,420 --> 00:36:23,530
I trust your ability,

850
00:36:24,570 --> 00:36:25,780
but he is not an ordinary man.

851
00:36:26,090 --> 00:36:27,300
Father is the Prefect.

852
00:36:27,900 --> 00:36:28,940
Treating him

853
00:36:28,940 --> 00:36:29,920
is not a trivial matter.

854
00:36:30,650 --> 00:36:33,020
Besides, you don't know his condition.

855
00:36:33,650 --> 00:36:34,860
What if something goes wrong

856
00:36:34,860 --> 00:36:35,940
during treatment?

857
00:36:36,250 --> 00:36:37,250
If Father punishes us,

858
00:36:37,650 --> 00:36:38,900
what will we do?

859
00:36:39,380 --> 00:36:40,220
Trust me.

860
00:36:41,020 --> 00:36:42,460
Before the envoys arrive,

861
00:36:43,090 --> 00:36:44,130
I'll do everything I can

862
00:36:44,570 --> 00:36:45,650
to finish the crossbow

863
00:36:46,170 --> 00:36:47,620
and solve Father's immediate problem.

